            .box.block.col-sm-6
              h2 NFL Passer Rating
              p#daysAgo
              p#updateDaysAgo
              p
                | Check out my NFL Passer Rating I made with Java. A GUI made from NetBeans, please follow the instructions to download and give it a whirl. Must have Java installed on your computer for it to work.
              p
              h3
                a.btn(href='http://nfl-passer-rating.bodiewebdesign.com/', role='button') Check Me Out! &raquo;
              p
          .row
            .box.block.col-sm-6.links
              img.img-responsive(src='static/img/grandcanyon.jpg', alt='Grand Canyon', width='400', height='300')
            .box.block.col-sm-6
              h2 Adam Hits the Big 3-0
              p#daysAgo1
              p#updateDaysAgo1
              p
                | Check out Adam&apos;s 30th Birthday Celebration at the Grand Canyon! Enjoy all the pictures and videos Adam and the Bodie family took at the Grand Canyon and surrounding areas, and don&apos;t forget to read Adam&apos;s interesting facts about the Grand Canyon and surrounding area. A trip in itself, without actually going there (if you can&apos;t, of course, you should if you can).
              p
              h3
                a.btn(href='http://grand-canyon.bodiewebdesign.com', role='button') Check Me Out! &raquo;
              p
          .row
            .box.block.col-sm-6.links
              img.img-responsive(src='static/img/redvelvet.jpg', alt='Red Velvet', width='400', height='300')
            .box.block.col-sm-6
              h2 Jenn&apos;s Birthday
              p#daysAgo2
              p#updateDaysAgo2
              p
                | My Sister Jenn is a wonderful soul. She knows how to have fun. On this project, I show off Jenn having fun with her wonderful peeps in her second home, Maryland. Whether it&apos;s putting on a nice smile or picking a statue&apos;s nose, Jenn is always the delight of any party, and one of the nicest people you would ever meet.
              p
              h3
                a.btn(href='http://birthday.bodiewebdesign.com', role='button') Check Me Out! &raquo;
              p
          .row
            .box.block.col-sm-6.links
              img.img-responsive(src='static/img/beer.jpg', alt='Breweries', width='400', height='300')
            .box.block.col-sm-6
              h2 Great Breweries in Oregon
              p#daysAgo3
              p#updateDaysAgo3
              p
                | One passion I&apos;ve developed over the past four years is Beer-culture. Living in a city with over 40 microbreweries on site alone, it&apos;s no wonder that Oregon is one of the best states for tasty craft beer. Here, you will find out the best breweries that I&apos;ve come across in Oregon.
              p
              h3
                a.btn(href='http://brewery.bodiewebdesign.com', role='button') Check Me Out! &raquo;
              p
          .row
            .box.block.col-sm-6.links
              img.img-responsive(src='static/img/ashland.jpg', alt='Ashland', width='400', height='300')
            .box.block.col-sm-6
              h2 Visit Ashland, Oregon
              p#daysAgo4
              p#updateDaysAgo4
              p
                | Once upon a time, I took a trip to Southern Oregon, where he visited the cities in the area, including Ashland. It was a nice trip, and although it was smoky and hazy by the time I got to Ashland, I managed to get a fascinating sun-smoked image of the Elizabethan Stage at the Oregon Shakespeare Festival. It inspired me to make a little web application about why you should visit Ashland
              p
              h3
                a.btn(href='http://ashland.bodiewebdesign.com', role='button') Check Me Out! &raquo;
              p
          .row
            .box.block.col-sm-6.links
              img.img-responsive(src='static/img/fortune.jpg', alt='Read Your Fortune Cookie', width='400', height='300')
            .box.block.col-sm-6
              h2 Read your Fortune Cookie
              p#daysAgo5
              p#updateDaysAgo5
              p
                | A simple yet mind boggling app that gives you a fortune cookie to read. All you got to do is fill in your name and age, and let the app do the rest. Don&apos;t you love 21st Century Single Page Application Technology. You never know what your fortune cookie will tell you! It&apos;s that simple! Trust me.
              p
              h3
                a.btn(href='http://fortune-cookie.bodiewebdesign.com', role='button') Check Me Out! &raquo;
              p
          .row
            .box.block.col-sm-6.links
