            .box.block.col-sm-6
              h2 Duck vs. Blue Hen!
              p#daysAgo6
              p#updateDaysAgo6
              p
                | In an epic battle of the ages, we compare the Duck and the Blue Hen by comparing their state of choice. One the one end, we have the Duck representing Oregon. The other, it&apos;s Blue Hen representing Delaware. We find out who&apos;s better by comparing the states down to the core. So whose side are you on?
              p
              h3
