            .box.block.col-sm-6.links
              img.img-responsive(src='static/img/compton.jpg', alt='Compton', width='400', height='300')
            .box.block.col-sm-6
              h2 Compton: A Soundtrack by Dr. Dre
              p#daysAgo7
              p#updateDaysAgo7
              p
                | Surprise surprise. Dr. Dre finally released his third and final album. And no, it&apos;s not Detox. Check out my review of Dr. Dre&apos;s new album, and a synopsis of his career that led up to this point.
              p
              h3
