              p#daysAgo8
              p#updateDaysAgo8
              p
                | Straight outta my vault: A collection of videos I&apos;ve taken over the years mostly ignored. Now available as a montage of everything Me. Come check it out and see everything I&apos;ve done in video!
              p
              h3
