              img.img-responsive(src='static/img/small.jpg', alt='Great Small Towns', width='400', height='300')
            .box.block.col-sm-6
              h2 Great Small Towns
              p#daysAgo9
              p#updateDaysAgo9
              p
                | Yes, it&apos;s always fun to visit the big city lights. But what would happen if the massive crowds and noise got too much for you? That&apos;s why you should appreciate the finest in small town tourism. You may be surprised by how much is out there.
              p
              h3
