            .box.block.col-sm-6
              h2 Overview of the Nama Language
              p#daysAgo13
              p#updateDaysAgo13
              p
                | During my senior year of college at the University of Minnesota, I took a Linguistics class and had to write a final paper on a language of my choice. I chose Nama, a Khoisan langauge in Africa that&apos;s known for their click consonants. With that said, here is my 25 page paper turned into an Ember.js backed web project.
              h3
                a.btn(href='http://nama.bodiewebdesign.com', role='button') Check Me Out &raquo;
              p
